						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Frequent Repairs</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						If you're calling for repairs multiple times a year or facing a major repair that costs more than half the
						price of a new system, replacement is often more cost-effective in the long run.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Rising Energy Bills -->
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
