						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Outdated Technology</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Older systems lack the advanced features and efficiency of modern HVAC technology. Upgrading can provide
						benefits like smart thermostats, zoned cooling and heating, improved air quality, and significant energy
						savings.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 text-center">
				<p class="text-lg text-darkgray max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
